List providers, description, year and link

get_metrics_metadata.Rd

This function allows you to list the list of available providers of the land4health package.

Usage

get_metrics_metadata(query = NULL)

Arguments

query

A string. Default is NULL. List of available providers. For more details, use the get_providers function.

Value

A tibble object.

Examples

# \donttest{
library(land4health)
get_metrics_metadata()
